Once the performance starts, the real fun begins: you can fling items at the stage, set off pyrotechnics and other cool effects, and even cheer (or boo) your squad. Seeing the payoffâan awesome video you can shareâwill encourage players to jump right back in and start working on their next great show.

Nothing beats a kid-friendly game that keeps the whole family captivatedâand Toca has us snipping, straightening, and styling to our heart's content. Once we've perfected our customer's silly new âdos, we make sure to add some accessories, snap a pic, and share the hair.
